<h1 class="entry-title">Why Assumptions About ‘Rising Inequality’ Are Wrong</h1>
<div class="entry-author">
			written by <a href="https://quillette.com/author/neema-parvini/" title="All posts by Neema Parvini">Neema Parvini</a> </div><!-- end .entry-author -->
