<div class="comment-text">
<p>“The article also doesn’t address the concentration of wealth at the very top. You don’t have to be a dyed-in-the-wool Marxist to be concerned when 1 per cent of people own more than half the wealth in the world, and the proportion that 1 per cent owns is rising relentlessly.”</p>
